textContent:
---aftereffects 4---

The last three days were amazing Rei! I'm really grateful I got to experience what if feels like to be able to see you for consecutive days and J. Christ, if this is an indicator of what the future holds, then I'm even more excited than ever. I love you so so so much babycakes!!!! I'm so happy I got to experience sleeping at night after being with you for the whole day and then sleep knowing that I'll see you again when I wake up. 

I miss you so much already baby! Grabe ang lala ng relapse ngayon HAHAHAHA. I could feel na its worse than all the previous relpases I've had before. Sabi ko na talaga, patay ako ng sabado eh HAHAHAHA. I could feel myself wanting to see you harder than ever, I miss you sosososo much. And the fact na magkikita tayo ulit after 8 days pa just makes it worse. Huhuhu. Iiyak nalang talaga ako HAHAHAHA. I need to see a therapist now. Jk. OA amp HAHAHAHAHA. Ang OA ko ngayon Rei grabe AHAHAHAHAHA. Ano to, hormones?!! HAHAHA. Feel ko ambilis ko mairita (sa ibang bagay ofc, not with you), tas I miss you so much pa. BAT NAGKAKAGANTO AKO GRRRRR HAHAHSHSHSHS. Ewan ko na HAHAHAHAHA nasisiraan nako ng bait bby kasalanan mo HHAHAHAHA. Kaya kasalanan mo talaga to, bawal mo nako talaga iwan tsaka pagpalit huhu. Mwaaaa.
